{"tid":864869,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★片】港鐵大故障：兩躁男樂富站內打架","createTime":"2018-10-16T13:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T02:11:57.000Z","uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7f78302921637049dab77de60249fc7df39596cb","tid":864869,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T13:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181016/photo/bkn-20181016191846561-1016_00822_001_01b.jpg?20181016204235\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181016%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181016191846561-1016_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20181016204235&h=5eed970a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片 : inside the link<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=OBK181016-14825-40-M&amp;d=1539692823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Fhk%2Findex.html%3Fi%3DOBK181016-14825-40-M%26d%3D1539692823&d=rLE2b5LvftGRA%2BEF0v4VpuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=1043290c\" target=\"_blank\">http://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=OBK181016-14825-40-M&amp;d=1539692823</a><br />\n<br />\n港鐵今晨（16日）4條路線齊「冧檔」，沿線車站逼爆，乘客之間有身體碰撞實屬無可避免，惟於早上10時許，觀塘線樂富站內，竟有2名男子因此而發生口角，繼而動武，兩人拳來腳往互不相讓，據讀者提供的片段可見，2名男子扭作一團，其中較年輕一位正流鼻血，而「阿叔」則上衣幾被扯甩，2人大聲指罵對方，在旁乘客則「眼望望」，有的拿出手機拍片，一名港鐵職員到場處理事件，制止並分隔他們。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，經初步調查後，拘捕2名分別姓周（30歲）及姓葉（60歲）男子，由於2人報稱鼻及頸等受傷，送院治理，警方將案件列作在公眾地方打架，交黃大仙警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181016/bkn-20181016191846561-1016_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181016%2Fbkn-20181016191846561-1016_00822_001.html&d=rLE2b5LvftGRA%2BEF0v4VpuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=7d38ded8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181016/bkn-20181016191846561-1016_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"19fe5a1a9817664a7ff3f501e73d35ffed3a9a90","tid":864869,"uid":68143,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T13:54:30.00